description: Those who attend Northern Illinois University don’t have to eat like typical college students, they get to put the ramen away and sustain their brains with nutritious, delicious, and affordable meals, thanks to Rolling Harvest Food Truck.Chef Jim, with his extensive culinary and dietetic expertise, is serving this lucky campus a tasty selection of wraps, sliders, salads (and more!) all made with locally sourced produce and mindfully sourced meats. Crowd favorites include the falafel slider and wrap- with fresh tomato, hummus, and tzatziki sauce.For all this and much more, have Rolling Harvest Food Truck roll on over to your next event and feed your guests this beautiful bounty!
name: Rolling Harvest Food Truck
